WEBVTT

00:09:29.996 --> 00:09:32.412
Bu qiyin narsalarni aytish vaqti
kelganda, men

00:09:32.412 --> 00:09:34.079
o’zimdan uchta savolni so’rayman.

00:09:34.079 --> 00:09:35.912
Bir: Uni nazarda tutdingmi?

00:09:36.496 --> 00:09:38.621
Ikki: Uni himoya qila olasanmi?

00:09:39.204 --> 00:09:41.329
Uch: Uni sevgi bilan aytdingmi?

00:09:41.371 --> 00:09:43.579
Agar uchalasiga ham “ha” javobi bo’lsa,
men

00:09:43.621 --> 00:09:45.496
buni aytaman
va oqibatidan qo’rqmayman.

00:09:47.537 --> 00:09:48.704
Bu muhim.

00:09:48.704 --> 00:09:50.246
Bu nazorat nuqtasi menga doimo:

00:09:50.246 --> 00:09:52.954
“Ha, sen buni qilishing kerak”,
deb ta’kidlaydi.

00:09:54.579 --> 00:09:56.996
Haqiqatni gapirish-mulohazali haqiqatni-
inqilobiy

00:09:56.996 --> 00:09:58.787
harakat bo’lishi shart emas.